import React from "react";
import {
  Navbar,
  Nav,
  Container,
  NavDropdown,
  Form,
  FormControl,
  Button,
} from "react-bootstrap";
import "../style/Navigation.css";

export default function Navigation(props) {
  return (
    <Navbar
      collapseOnSelect
      expand="lg"
      bg="light"
      variant="light"
      className="p-3"
    >
      <Container>
        <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Linh Klatt</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
          <Nav className="me-auto">
            <Nav.Link
              href="#home"
              className="custom-nav"
              onClick={() => props.handlePageChange("Home")}
            >
              Home
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link
              href="#link"
              className="custom-nav"
              onClick={() => props.handlePageChange("Link")}
            >
              Link
            </Nav.Link>
            <NavDropdown title="Dropdown" id="collasible-nav-dropdown">
              <NavDropdown.Item
                href="#action/3.1"
                onClick={() => props.handlePageChange("Action")}
              >
                Action
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item
                href="#action/3.2"
                onClick={() => props.handlePageChange("AnotherAction")}
              >
                Another action
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Divider />
              <NavDropdown.Item
                href="#action/3.4"
                onClick={() => props.handlePageChange("SomethingElse")}
              >
                Something else here
              </NavDropdown.Item>
            </NavDropdown>
          </Nav>
          <Nav>
            <Nav.Link
              href="#about-me"
              className="custom-nav"
              onClick={() => props.handlePageChange("AboutMe")}
            >
              About Me
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link
              href="#skills"
              className="custom-nav"
              onClick={() => props.handlePageChange("Skills")}
            >
              Skills
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link
              href="#projects"
              className="custom-nav"
              onClick={() => props.handlePageChange("Projects")}
            >
              Projects
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link
              href="#contact"
              className="custom-nav"
              onClick={() => props.handlePageChange("Contact")}
            >
              Contact
            </Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link
              href="#resume"
              className="custom-nav"
              onClick={() => props.handlePageChange("Resume")}
            >
              Resume
            </Nav.Link>
          </Nav>
          <Form className="d-flex">
            <FormControl
              type="search"
              placeholder="Search"
              className="me-2"
              aria-label="Search"
            />
            <Button variant="outline-success">Search</Button>
          </Form>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
}
